<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawpi ah zan ahung hi a,
 Suna mipi tamna leh;
 Kiko thawma dimna mun chuh,
 Khawlai chuh a hung thip a;
 Thachawl taka khuolzin mite,
 Isu thu gen vielte chuh;
 Suongkul sungnung a khum ahiu,
 Gamsung vaihawmpa thu chun.

[V2]
 2. Tam takvei zepin a um ui,
 Sapsiet na tincheng thuokin;
 Kawt tamtak kamkhuma um in,
 A keng uh a kawl butin;
 Rom suongkul veng, migilopa,
 Mi dang cheng a ih sung un;
 Khawvak tunga thilmak tung ding,
 He phalo in a um hi.

[V3]
 3. Ngaiin, suongkul tangte tau git,
 Ngeihtak, sawttak kiko in;
 Ngeih deuh deuh leh chien takin gen,
 Paucham lasak git ahi!
 Suongkul bang a hung kithing a,
 Kawtkhak a hung kihawnga!
 Ngaiun lei a hung kilinga,
 Mitin kawlbuh a kiphel!

[V4]
 4. Aw, mun thawmhauh um a um puoi,
 Lasak gitin a thawng thei;
 Aw lungkham umna zan umlo,
 Paucham leng hatna um ding;
 La sa'n, la sa'n, khuolzin thachawl,
 Van lungmuonna chuh mu'n la;
 Suongkul tang gikpuo, paucham in,
 Lalpa'n hun puidawk ina.</lyrics>
<title>PAULAND SILAS</title>
<hymn_number>347</hymn_number>
</song>